<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!--Uploaded in SOA repository on 2014-06-27 09:33:34.481--><!--SOA repository reference: W001165-v1.0.0--><xsd:schema xmlns:xsd="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema" xmlns:tns="http://www.af-klm.com/services/common/AlteaConversation-v1/xsd" elementFormDefault="qualified" targetNamespace="http://www.af-klm.com/services/common/AlteaConversation-v1/xsd">
   <xsd:element name="Conversation" type="tns:Conversation"/>
   <xsd:complexType name="Conversation">
   		<xsd:annotation>
<xsd:documentation>
The behaviour related to the conversation of the service depends on the values of "SessionID" and "Conversation required" in the request:
"SessionID" 	"Conversation required" 	Behaviour for provider side adapter
  Empty	        Start							Creates a conversation or reuses a conversation, returns a Conversation ID, calls the service.
  Empty         Stop							Will return a SOAP Fault: "Conversation stop required but no Conversation ID provided"
  Empty         None              Default for the service. No conversation is required.
  Filled        Start             Will return a SOAP Fault: "Conversation must be started with an empty Conversation ID"
  Filled        Stop              Clears the conversation on provider, the Conversation ID is returned to the 'pool'; errors can be SOAP Fault: "This conversation is not active" or "Trying to stop a conversation not belonging to you".
  Filled        Continue	        Calls the service; errors can be SOAP Fault: "This conversation is not active" or "Trying to use a conversation not belonging to you"
  Filled        None              Will return a SOAP Fault: "Action is not compatible with conversation"
</xsd:documentation>
   		</xsd:annotation>
			<xsd:sequence>
				<xsd:element minOccurs="0" name="Id" type="xsd:string"/>
				<xsd:element name="ConversationRequired">
					<xsd:simpleType>
						<xsd:restriction base="xsd:string">
							<xsd:enumeration value="None"/>
							<xsd:enumeration value="Start"/>
							<xsd:enumeration value="Continue"/>
							<xsd:enumeration value="Stop"/>
						</xsd:restriction>
					</xsd:simpleType>
				</xsd:element>
			</xsd:sequence>
   </xsd:complexType>
</xsd:schema>